snippet.title: VIDEOVERSE – First Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Get a first look at the gameplay of VIDEOVERSE – Coming 2023!

----------------------

Take a trip back to the days of the early internet and fan forums, when the video game console "Kinmoku Shark" and its online social network "Videoverse" were still popular...

Download VIDEOVERSE on...
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2079180/VIDEOVERSE/
itch.io: https://kinmoku.itch.io/videoverse
Humble: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/videoverse

More information and press-kit available at: https://gamesbykinmoku.com/videoverse
